{"tid":2011181,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你 你班玩具撚柒撚完未？","createTime":"2020-05-10T22:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T03:50:10.000Z","uid":5190,"like":62,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58976f928af0d6505d772a0f4db8204c6f598586","tid":2011181,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:48:40.000Z","msg":"得啦知你係班小朋友為咗證明玩具唔係玩具而話足波係玩具啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑幾步又入波跑幾步又入波 成個場我十步跑撚晒 仲細撚過我屋企 唔通我平時係屋企行嚟行去又做緊運動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打下手仔又嗌foul 成個女人咁 又乜春搏盡無悔 懶係感性  屌你老母好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係人都知籃球係玩具 原本都無乜人得閒理鳩你班傻閪 無啦啦又要係到嘈 嘈撚完又係柒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如收收皮 繼續係室內冷氣地方行幾步路玩下籃波仔啦<br />\n<br />\n再唔係嘅咪成個弱智咁 幻想下自己係乜乜柒占咁 行行下街轉身射個三分波囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係隔離我一定要拍撚晒手掌 再讚係射得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評 支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評 樓主講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a1c9bacf396c86f4b0c2474e18de10d8dba978","tid":2011181,"uid":125502,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"a749494deb612e16429fbf601c5ee917061de0a7","tid":2011181,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02a1c9bacf396c86f4b0c2474e18de10d8dba978","tid":2011181,"uid":125502,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:51:39.000Z","msg":"好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b414135e5db605a8e2c7c2b8382798e2c820602","tid":2011181,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17046f28fd6e9d598e4044460ca94e39dfa2ee9","tid":2011181,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b414135e5db605a8e2c7c2b8382798e2c820602","tid":2011181,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf0751eb54b